{"id":130,"parent_id":124,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":130,"title":"Romans 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rom.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","Baptism is in similitude of the death, burial, and resurrection of Christ—The wages of sin is death—Christ brings eternal life."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.1","order":"03.08.006.15436"},["b","1"],"What shall we say then? Shall we continue in sin, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"grace"],"may abound?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.2","order":"03.08.006.15437"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"God forbid"],". How shall we, that are dead to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"sin"],", live any longer therein?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.3","order":"03.08.006.15438"},["b","3"],"Know ye not, that so many of us as were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"baptized"],"into Jesus Christ were baptized into his death?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.4","order":"03.08.006.15439"},["b","4"],"Therefore we are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"buried"],"with him by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"baptism"],"into death: that like as Christ was raised up from the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"dead"],"by the glory of the Father, even so we also should",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"walk"],"in",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_4e"},"newness"],"of life."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.5","order":"03.08.006.15440"},["b","5"],"For if we have been planted together in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"likeness"],"of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"death"],", we shall be also",["i","in the likeness"],"of",["i","his"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"resurrection"],":"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.6","order":"03.08.006.15441"},["b","6"],"Knowing this, that our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"old"],"man is crucified with",["i","him,"],"that the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"body"],"of sin might be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"destroyed"],", that henceforth we should not serve",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.7","order":"03.08.006.15442"},["b","7"],"For he that is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"dead"],"is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"freed"],"from sin."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.8","order":"03.08.006.15443"},["b","8"],"Now if we be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"dead"],"with Christ, we believe that we shall also live with him:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.9","order":"03.08.006.15444"},["b","9"],"Knowing that Christ being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"raised"],"from the dead dieth no more; death hath no more dominion over him."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.10","order":"03.08.006.15445"},["b","10"],"For in that he died, he died unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"sin"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"once"],": but in that he liveth, he liveth unto God."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.11","order":"03.08.006.15446"},["b","11"],"Likewise reckon ye also yourselves to be dead indeed unto sin, but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"alive"],"unto God through Jesus Christ our Lord."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.12","order":"03.08.006.15447"},["b","12"],"Let not sin therefore reign in your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"mortal"],"body, that ye should obey it in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"lusts"],"thereof."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.13","order":"03.08.006.15448"},["b","13"],"Neither",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"yield"],"ye your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"members"],["i","as"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"instruments"],"of unrighteousness unto sin: but",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"yield"],"yourselves unto God, as those that are alive from the dead, and your members",["i","as"],"instruments of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_13e"},"righteousness"],"unto God."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.14","order":"03.08.006.15449"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"For sin"],"shall not have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"dominion"],"over you: for ye are not under the law, but under grace."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.15","order":"03.08.006.15450"},["b","15"],"What then? shall we sin, because we are not under the law, but under",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"grace"],"?",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"God forbid"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.16","order":"03.08.006.15451"},["b","16"],"Know ye not, that to whom ye yield yourselves",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"servants"],"to obey, his servants ye are to whom ye",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"obey"],"; whether of sin unto death, or of obedience unto righteousness?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.17","order":"03.08.006.15452"},["b","17"],"But God be thanked, that ye were the servants of sin, but ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"obeyed"],"from the heart that form of doctrine which was delivered you."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.18","order":"03.08.006.15453"},["b","18"],"Being then made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"free"],"from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"sin"],", ye became the servants of righteousness."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.19","order":"03.08.006.15454"},["b","19"],"I speak after the manner of men because of the infirmity of your flesh: for as ye have yielded your members servants to uncleanness and to iniquity unto iniquity; even so now yield your members servants to righteousness unto holiness."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.20","order":"03.08.006.15455"},["b","20"],"For when ye were the servants of sin, ye were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"free from"],"righteousness."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.21","order":"03.08.006.15456"},["b","21"],"What",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"fruit"],"had ye then in those things whereof ye are now ashamed? for the end of those things",["i","is"],"death."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.22","order":"03.08.006.15457"},["b","22"],"But now being made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"free"],"from sin, and become servants to God, ye have your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"fruit"],"unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"holiness"],", and the end everlasting life."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.23","order":"03.08.006.15458"},["b","23"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"wages"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"sin"],["i","is"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"death"],"; but the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_23d"},"gift"],"of God",["i","is"],["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_23e"},"eternal life"],"through Jesus Christ our Lord."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.1a","order":"03.08.006.15459"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.32.29-34"},"D&C 20:32 (29–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.2a","order":"03.08.006.15461"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"May it not be!"],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.2b","order":"03.08.006.15463"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.41"},"Mosiah 2:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.3a","order":"03.08.006.15465"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.25"},"Mosiah 27:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.4a","order":"03.08.006.15467"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-immersion"},"TG Baptism, Immersion"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.4b","order":"03.08.006.15469"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism"},"TG Baptism"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.4c","order":"03.08.006.15471"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-death-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Death of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.4d","order":"03.08.006.15473"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"4e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.4e","order":"03.08.006.15475"},["b","4e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-qualifications-for"},"TG Baptism, Qualifications for"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-new-spiritually-reborn"},"Man, New, Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.5a","order":"03.08.006.15477"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-memory"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Memory"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.5b","order":"03.08.006.15479"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.20"},"Col. 2:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/3.3"},"3:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/2.11"},"2 Tim. 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.5c","order":"03.08.006.15481"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.6a","order":"03.08.006.15483"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.22.22-24"},"Eph. 4:22 (22–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/3.9"},"Col. 3:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.6b","order":"03.08.006.15485"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.11"},"Col. 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.6c","order":"03.08.006.15487"},["b","6c"],["span.small","GR"],"brought to an end, freed."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.6d","order":"03.08.006.15489"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.32.32-33"},"Moro. 10:32 (32–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.7a","order":"03.08.006.15491"},["b","7a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rom. 6:7 … dead",["i","to sin"],"…"],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.7b","order":"03.08.006.15493"},["b","7b"],["span.small","GR"],"acquitted, cleared."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.8a","order":"03.08.006.15495"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-death-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Death of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.9a","order":"03.08.006.15497"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.10a","order":"03.08.006.15499"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.28"},"Heb. 9:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.10b","order":"03.08.006.15501"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/7.27"},"Heb. 7:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.10"},"10:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.11a","order":"03.08.006.15503"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/2.19"},"Gal. 2:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.12a","order":"03.08.006.15505"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mortality"},"TG Mortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.12b","order":"03.08.006.15507"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.13a","order":"03.08.006.15509"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.27.27-28"},"2 Ne. 4:27 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.13b","order":"03.08.006.15511"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/3.5"},"Col. 3:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.13c","order":"03.08.006.15513"},["b","13c"],["span.small","GR"],"weapons."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.13d","order":"03.08.006.15515"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.19"},"Mosiah 3:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/3.35"},"Hel. 3:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"13e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.13e","order":"03.08.006.15517"},["b","13e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.14a","order":"03.08.006.15519"},["b","14a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rom. 6:14 For",["i","in so doing"],"sin …"],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.14b","order":"03.08.006.15521"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.29.26-29"},"2 Ne. 2:29 (26–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.15a","order":"03.08.006.15523"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.15b","order":"03.08.006.15525"},["b","15b"],["span.small","GR"],"May it not be!"],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.16a","order":"03.08.006.15527"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.34"},"John 8:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.16b","order":"03.08.006.15529"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/3.27.26-27"},"Alma 3:27 (26–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.34.33-36"},"34:34 (33–36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/14.31.29-31"},"Hel. 14:31 (29–31)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/obedience"},"TG Obedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.17a","order":"03.08.006.15531"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commitment"},"TG Commitment"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.18a","order":"03.08.006.15533"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",